Package: comparpq
Type: Package
Title: Compare and Analyse Multiple 'phyloseq' Objects
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: person("Adrien", "Taudière", email = "adrien.taudiere@zaclys.net",
  role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1088-1182"))
Description: Compare and analyse multiple 'phyloseq' objects from the 'R'
  'phyloseq' package. Provides tools for taxonomic comparison, accuracy
  metrics computation (confusion matrix approach with FDR, TPR, F1 score,
  and MCC), and visualizations including bubble plots, Venn diagrams, and
  diversity estimation across groups of microbiome datasets.
